        div(id='header')
          div(class='center')
            h1(class='scalingHeader') Slice of Pacific

    div(class='container h-100')
      div(class='row h-100 justify-content-center align-items-center screenHeight')
        div(class='col-xs-3 col-no-padding')
          div(class='content_area text-center')
            form
              a(href='/login' class='scalingButtons green_background btn btn-success') Sign In!
              div(class='row m-1')
              img(src="/public/images/pizza.svg" class='scalingImage')
              div(class='row m-1')
              a(href='/users/new' class='scalingButtons green_background btn btn-success') Don't have an account?

